{"tid":944692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(phy攞5**入)如果閃電俠用光速跑緊步，超人要追上佢，咪姐係超光速？","createTime":"2018-12-17T10:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T11:09:21.000Z","uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc742ef6085f0c59b348cefd9a6d850befd2816a","tid":944692,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"超光速情況下，超人會睇到倒後既影像，佢會見到倒後行既閃電俠<br />\n<br />\n但實際佢倒後行返去搵閃電俠，只係追個影，閃電俠依然係光速跑緊<br />\n<br />\n最後超人要幾次來回先追到閃電俠，頂多並排，唔可以扒頭<br />\n<br />\n我有冇諗錯？"},{"pid":"ed3d07c1f35c30e2d9463ff9f3f88b69e7393b45","tid":944692,"uid":178883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"光速可以時光倒流 但倒流應該都有個速度 而超光速等於倒退嘅速度更快 有咩咁難明 姐係超光速個dT/dt大過光速個dT/dt"},{"pid":"f8a247033443fa2794523c04e749706ec56020aa","tid":944692,"uid":186072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"冇諗錯<br />\n你用F=ma 就會計到你既講法係正確<br />\n利申 phy5**"},{"pid":"117da53d186091d3ef81bc67a4310092f76aa1fc","tid":944692,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a247033443fa2794523c04e749706ec56020aa","tid":944692,"uid":186072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"冇諗錯<br />\n你用F=ma 就會計到你既講法係正確<br />\n利申 phy5**"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdd78cad9babd1a98071146dfb86ee3332e179c","tid":944692,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1d21ba6b5ece941e9f13efde50d41c54c91d1fb","tid":944692,"uid":71238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afdd78cad9babd1a98071146dfb86ee3332e179c","tid":944692,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a247033443fa2794523c04e749706ec56020aa","tid":944692,"uid":186072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"冇諗錯<br />\n你用F